<bibRefCitation author="Larochelle, A. &amp; M. - C. Lariviere" box="[345,754,898,922]" pageId="48" pageNumber="47" pagination="1 - 281" refId="ref33655" refString="Larochelle, A., and M. - C. Lariviere. 2001. Carabidae (Insecta: Coleoptera): catalogue. Fauna of New Zealand 43: 1 - 281." type="journal article" year="2001">Larochelle and Larivière 2001: 83</bibRefCitation>
(catalogue; biology, dispersal power, ecology, geographic distribution, reference).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="48" pageNumber="47" type="discussion">
